WEBVTT

00:05.939 --> 00:08.076
announcer:
IN THE CRIMINAL JUSTICE SYSTEM,

00:08.109 --> 00:11.745
SEXUALLY BASED OFFENSES ARE
CONSIDERED ESPECIALLY HEINOUS.

00:11.779 --> 00:14.215
IN NEW YORK CITY,
THE DEDICATED DETECTIVES

00:14.248 --> 00:16.184
WHO INVESTIGATE
THESE VICIOUS FELONIES

00:16.217 --> 00:17.418
ARE MEMBERS OF AN ELITE SQUAD

00:17.451 --> 00:19.520
KNOWN AS
THE SPECIAL VICTIMS UNIT.

00:19.553 --> 00:22.022
THESE ARE THEIR STORIES.

00:23.191 --> 00:24.758
- GOOD EVENING.

00:24.792 --> 00:28.529
FOR THE NEXT TWO HOURS
WE WILL TAKE YOU WITH US

00:28.562 --> 00:31.532
INTO ANOTHER WORLD.

00:31.565 --> 00:34.368
THE WORLD OF THE FLESH.

00:34.402 --> 00:38.072
- TED, I'M TRYING TO PREPARE.
- I WON'T STAY LONG.

00:38.106 --> 00:41.409
HERE.
FOR YOUR FIRST OPENING.

00:41.442 --> 00:44.078
YOU HAVE A LOT OF ADMIRERS.

00:44.112 --> 00:46.480
- I SHOULD TAKE A PICTURE
FOR MY SCRAPBOOK.

00:46.514 --> 00:48.682
- YOU HAVE A SCRAPBOOK?
- YEAH.

00:48.716 --> 00:52.620
- SERIOUSLY?
- COMING TO NEW YORK...

00:52.653 --> 00:55.156
GETTING THIS SHOW,
I JUST...

00:55.189 --> 00:57.525
KEEP THINKING
IT'S ALL BEEN A DREAM.

00:57.558 --> 00:59.393
- THIS IS FOR REAL, MEGHAN.

00:59.427 --> 01:02.430
MOST OF THE CRITICS
ARE COMING TONIGHT.

01:02.463 --> 01:06.400
YOUR LIFE WILL NEVER
BE THE SAME.

01:08.802 --> 01:11.272
BREAK A LEG.
- THANKS.

01:11.305 --> 01:14.408
- HOW DO YOU ENVISION YOURSELF?
AN ELEPHANT?

01:14.442 --> 01:16.677
A MONKEY?

01:16.710 --> 01:18.546
NO.

01:18.579 --> 01:20.548
YOU'RE A HAWK.

01:20.581 --> 01:24.285
- NO ONE HERE
WILL KNOW YOU.

01:24.318 --> 01:27.321
NO ONE HERE WILL JUDGE YOU.

01:27.355 --> 01:31.692
[Gregorian chants
set to a dance beat]

01:31.725 --> 01:35.896
- STRIP OFF
YOUR INHIBITIONS.

01:35.929 --> 01:43.371
*

01:43.404 --> 01:49.777
SEE CARNAL PLEASURE
AND JOIN IN.

01:49.810 --> 01:53.681
TOUCH THE WORLD
OF THE FLESH.

01:53.714 --> 01:57.318
THE WORLD OF THE FORBIDDEN.

01:57.351 --> 01:59.420
- LUST, BEAUTY.

01:59.453 --> 02:03.691
WHEN LOVE IS NOT MADNESS,
IT IS NOT LOVE.

02:03.724 --> 02:09.563
- RELEASE
YOUR DARKEST DESIRES.

02:09.597 --> 02:13.434
TASTE...

02:13.467 --> 02:16.604
TOUCH...

02:16.637 --> 02:19.207
TAKE...

02:19.240 --> 02:22.643
UNLEASH YOUR POWER.

02:22.676 --> 02:25.246
- PAOLO, HURRY!
WE'RE ALONE.

02:25.279 --> 02:26.780
- BUT YOUR HUSBAND.

02:26.814 --> 02:29.717
- GIOVANNI JUST LEFT.
- ARE YOU SURE?

02:29.750 --> 02:31.352
THEN KISS ME.

02:33.954 --> 02:35.789
- I AM BACK!

02:35.823 --> 02:39.627
FRANCESCA, WHAT THE HELL
IS GOING ON?

02:39.660 --> 02:41.962
GUARDS, GET OUT!
GUARDS, OUT!

02:41.995 --> 02:45.165
- GIOVANNI.
PAOLO, GO!

02:48.369 --> 02:51.472
[grunting]
GIOVANNI, WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

02:51.505 --> 02:53.774
- SHE BETRAYED YOU, GIOVANNI.
I SAW THE WHOLE THING.

02:53.807 --> 02:57.411
- [crying]
NO, LET GO OF ME!

02:57.445 --> 02:59.447
NO!

02:59.480 --> 03:01.982
HELP ME!

03:02.015 --> 03:04.485
SOMEBODY HELP ME!

03:10.291 --> 03:12.860
- MEGHAN!
WHAT HAPPENED?

03:12.893 --> 03:16.330
YOU MISSED THE FINALE.

03:16.364 --> 03:17.998
MEGHAN.

03:18.031 --> 03:20.501
ARE YOU OKAY?

03:20.534 --> 03:24.272
- I CAN'T REMEMBER
THE LAST TIME I WAS ON SKATES.

03:24.305 --> 03:26.006
- CAN'T REMEMBER THE LAST TIME
I DID ANYTHING

03:26.039 --> 03:29.710
OTHER THAN PREP WITNESSES
OR WRITE A PRE-TRIAL MOTION.

03:29.743 --> 03:31.312
- WELL, THIS WAS A START.
DO IT AGAIN?

03:31.345 --> 03:34.848
- YEAH.
- BENSON.

03:34.882 --> 03:37.251
YEAH.

03:37.285 --> 03:40.754
- NO, I BLAME MYSELF.
IT'S IMMERSIVE THEATER.

03:40.788 --> 03:42.990
I PUSHED THE PIECE
TO BE PROVOCATIVE

03:43.023 --> 03:45.693
AND OBVIOUSLY SOMEBODY
JUST TOOK IT TOO FAR.

03:45.726 --> 03:47.328
- WHOA, SLOW DOWN.

03:47.361 --> 03:50.498
YOU'RE SAYING THAT THE ACTRESS
WAS RAPED ON STAGE?

03:50.531 --> 03:53.000
- WHERE WAS THE AUDIENCE?
- THEY WERE WATCHING.

03:53.033 --> 03:55.369
THEY THOUGHT IT WAS PART
OF THE SHOW.

04:00.441 --> 04:03.444
[Law & Order theme]

04:03.477 --> 04:11.485
*

04:47.855 --> 04:50.758
- IT'S DANTE'S INFERNO...
KIND OF.

04:50.791 --> 04:53.427
I PLAY FRANCESCA.

04:53.461 --> 04:56.997
I SLEEP WITH MY HUSBAND'S
BROTHER PAOLO.

04:57.030 --> 05:00.934
WHOEVER DID THIS TO ME
WAS PRETENDING TO BE GIOVANNI--

05:00.968 --> 05:01.869
MY JEALOUS HUSBAND.

05:01.902 --> 05:04.438
- WHERE WAS THE ACTOR
PLAYING GIOVANNI?

05:04.472 --> 05:08.476
- HE'S NOT IN THIS SCENE.
IT'S JUST ME AND PAOLO.

05:08.509 --> 05:11.445
IT'S THE BETRAYAL.

05:11.479 --> 05:12.446
- A LITTLE EARLY FOR YOU
IN THE GAME,

05:12.480 --> 05:13.447
ISN'T IT, COUNSELOR?

05:13.481 --> 05:14.815
- I WAS IN THE NEIGHBORHOOD.

05:14.848 --> 05:16.016
- BENSON WITH THE VIC?

05:16.049 --> 05:17.785
- AMBULANCE IS ON ITS WAY.

05:17.818 --> 05:20.621
TED SCOTT, DIRECTOR.
DETECTIVE TUTUOLA.

05:20.654 --> 05:23.524
- HELLO.
- SO WHAT HAPPENED?

05:23.557 --> 05:27.561
- SOMEONE IN THE AUDIENCE
GOT CAUGHT UP IN THE THEATRICS.

05:27.595 --> 05:31.632
BELIEVED HE WAS GIOVANNI,
RAPING HIS WIFE IN REVENGE.

05:31.665 --> 05:34.134
- HOLD UP, PEOPLE IN THE SEATS
GET TO ACT WITH THE ACTORS?

05:34.167 --> 05:35.469
- THERE ARE NO SEATS.

05:35.503 --> 05:37.771
IT'S THEATER INTERACTIVE.

05:37.805 --> 05:41.709
THE AUDIENCE WALKS THROUGH
DANTE'S NINE CIRCLES OF HELL.

05:41.742 --> 05:46.447
- THE VICTIM WAS ATTACKED
IN THE SECOND CIRCLE--LUST.

05:46.480 --> 05:48.982
- CAN YOU TELL ME
WHAT HE DID TO YOU?

05:49.016 --> 05:52.453
- UH...

05:52.486 --> 05:58.559
AT FIRST, I JUST THOUGHT
HE WAS BEING WEIRD.

06:02.963 --> 06:08.469
- MEGHAN, DID HE RAPE YOU?

06:08.502 --> 06:11.439
- YES.

06:11.472 --> 06:14.942
- CAN YOU TELL ME ANYTHING
ABOUT YOUR ATTACKER?

06:14.975 --> 06:17.678
ANY KIND OF PHYSICALITY?

06:17.711 --> 06:20.481
- IT ALL HAPPENED SO FAST.

06:20.514 --> 06:22.850
HE WAS WEARING A GOAT MASK.

06:22.883 --> 06:25.719
- DO YOU KNOW HIS RACE?
WAS HE YOUNG, WAS HE OLD?

06:25.753 --> 06:27.988
- HE WAS WHITE.

06:28.021 --> 06:33.694
UM, SMELLED LIKE HE SMOKED.

06:33.727 --> 06:36.029
- DID HE HOLD YOUR WRISTS?

06:36.063 --> 06:37.998
- NO, THAT WAS SOMEONE ELSE.

06:38.031 --> 06:43.537
UM, HE WAS WEARING
A HAWK MASK.

06:43.571 --> 06:47.508
I JUST MOVED HERE
SIX MONTHS AGO.

06:47.541 --> 06:51.011
THIS IS THE FIRST PLAY
THAT I EVEN AUDITIONED FOR.

06:51.044 --> 06:55.849
I JUST--I CAN'T BELIEVE
THIS HAPPENED TO ME.

06:55.883 --> 06:57.918
- CAN ANYONE GET IN
ONCE THE SHOW STARTS?

06:57.951 --> 07:00.087
- NO, ALL THE DOORS
ARE COVERED.

07:00.120 --> 07:01.655
COMPLETELY COVERED.

07:01.689 --> 07:03.524
- OKAY, I'M GONNA NEED
ALL YOUR BOX OFFICE RECEIPTS

07:03.557 --> 07:05.593
AND CREDIT CARD SLIPS.

07:05.626 --> 07:07.861
- EVE, DO YOU MIND?

07:07.895 --> 07:11.599
- MEGHAN SAYS THAT HER ATTACKER
WAS WEARING A GOAT MASK.

07:11.632 --> 07:13.467
I TAKE IT YOU GET THOSE BACK
AT THE END OF THE NIGHT.

07:13.501 --> 07:15.102
- YES.
- OKAY, WE'RE GONNA NEED THOSE.

07:15.135 --> 07:16.103
AND THE ROPES TOO.

07:16.136 --> 07:18.906
AND CSU IS GONNA HAVE TO COMB
OVER YOUR SETS.

07:18.939 --> 07:20.608
- WE HAVE A SHOW TOMORROW.

07:20.641 --> 07:23.577
- NO, YOU DON'T.
THIS ISN'T A THEATER.

07:23.611 --> 07:27.581
IT'S A CRIME SCENE.

07:27.615 --> 07:29.650
- SMALL TOWN GIRL MOVES
TO THE CITY,

07:29.683 --> 07:32.986
HER FIRST JOB ON THE STAGE
AND SHE GETS RAPED.

07:33.020 --> 07:34.588
AUDIENCE APPLAUDS.

07:34.622 --> 07:35.723
NEW YORK IS JUST--

07:35.756 --> 07:38.125
- WELL, THIS KIND OF THING
IS WHY THE NEA WAS GUTTED.

07:38.158 --> 07:39.993
ANY SUSPECTS?

07:40.027 --> 07:41.795
- 150.

07:41.829 --> 07:43.196
IT WAS OPENING NIGHT,
THERE WAS A FULL HOUSE,

07:43.230 --> 07:44.832
AND EVERYONE WORE MASKS.

07:44.865 --> 07:46.166
- WELL, THAT'S JUST GREAT.

07:46.199 --> 07:47.267
- WE'RE TRACKING DOWN
EVERYONE WHO BOUGHT A TICKET

07:47.300 --> 07:49.637
BY CREDIT CARD,
AND SO FAR NO RECORDS,

07:49.670 --> 07:51.605
NO ONE
ON THE SEX OFFENDERS LIST.

07:51.639 --> 07:52.973
- DID YOU TALK TO ANYBODY
WHO WAS IN THE ROOM

07:53.006 --> 07:54.207
WHEN IT HAPPENED?

07:54.241 --> 07:55.576
- NONE THAT KNOW IT HAPPENED.

07:55.609 --> 07:57.978
IT WAS DARK.
THEY'D ALL HAD A FEW.

07:58.011 --> 07:59.747
THEY THOUGHT IT WAS PART
OF THE SHOW.

07:59.780 --> 08:01.749
- RAPE KIT'S IN.

08:01.782 --> 08:03.050
THERE'S NO TRAUMA,

08:03.083 --> 08:05.285
EXCEPT FOR WRIST ABRASIONS.
NO DNA.

08:05.318 --> 08:07.688
- IT WAS THEIR OPENING NIGHT.

08:07.721 --> 08:09.557
ANY CHANCE IT WAS ALL
FOR PUBLICITY?

08:09.590 --> 08:10.591
- THIS GIRL MEGHAN,

08:10.624 --> 08:12.560
SHE JUST MOVED HERE
FROM HENNEPIN, MINNESOTA,

08:12.593 --> 08:14.061
SIX MONTHS AGO.

08:14.094 --> 08:15.829
SHE'S PRETTY SHAKEN UP.

08:15.863 --> 08:17.497
- WELL, SHE IS AN ACTRESS.

08:20.067 --> 08:21.735
- POINT TAKEN.

08:23.904 --> 08:28.075
SEE IF HER STORY
HAS CHANGED OVERNIGHT.

08:31.979 --> 08:34.147
- LIV...WHAT WAS THAT ABOUT?

08:35.983 --> 08:38.886
WHAT, SHE'S AN ACTRESS,
SHE'S ON STAGE,

08:38.919 --> 08:40.654
SHE DRESSED PROVOCATIVELY,

08:40.688 --> 08:41.989
THAT MEANS SHE'S
AUTOMATICALLY LYING?

08:42.022 --> 08:43.624
- NO, THEY DON'T THINK THAT.

08:43.657 --> 08:45.158
- WELL, SOMETHING
WAS GOING ON.

08:45.192 --> 08:48.862
I ALSO KNOW
YOU HEARD IT TOO.

08:48.896 --> 08:50.864
I KEEP WANTING TO THINK
THAT THINGS HAVE CHANGED--

08:50.898 --> 08:51.932
- THEY HAVE CHANGED.

08:51.965 --> 08:53.801
COMPARED TO THE WAY
IT USED TO BE,

08:53.834 --> 08:56.269
THEY'VE CHANGED.

09:03.076 --> 09:04.912
- I TOLD YOU ALREADY.

09:04.945 --> 09:08.982
NO ONE I HAVE EVER KNOWN
WOULD DO ANYTHING LIKE THAT.

09:09.016 --> 09:12.152
- SO WHAT ABOUT SOMEBODY
THAT KNOWS YOU?

09:12.185 --> 09:14.187
A FAN?

09:14.221 --> 09:16.156
- LOOK, MEGHAN,
FROM WHAT YOU TELL US,

09:16.189 --> 09:18.291
IT SOUNDS LIKE
HE KNEW THE PLAY.

09:18.325 --> 09:20.761
HE TIMED HIS MOVE.

09:20.794 --> 09:23.764
- THERE ARE GUYS
WHO WAIT OUTSIDE THE STAGE DOOR

09:23.797 --> 09:26.033
FOR AN AUTOGRAPH.

09:26.066 --> 09:28.969
A COUPLE OF THEM I THINK
I'VE SEEN MORE THAN ONCE.

09:29.002 --> 09:31.271
- DO YOU KNOW
ANY OF THEIR NAMES?

09:31.304 --> 09:32.906
- NO.

09:32.940 --> 09:34.875
I JUST SMILE AT THEM.

09:38.378 --> 09:42.783
- OH, I'M SORRY.
- OH, IT'S OKAY.

09:42.816 --> 09:44.718
IT'S MY ROOMMATE.

09:44.752 --> 09:49.022
WE MOVED HERE TOGETHER
TO BE ACTRESSES.

09:49.056 --> 09:53.293
HEY, THEY THINK
IT WAS SOMEONE STALKING ME.

09:53.326 --> 09:56.864
- YOU MEAN, ONE OF
YOUR STAGE DOOR JOHNNIES?

09:56.897 --> 10:00.000
- OH, THANKS.

10:00.033 --> 10:02.770
- SO HAVE ANY OF THESE GUYS,
YOU KNOW, LEFT YOU MESSAGES?

10:02.803 --> 10:06.006
TRIED TO SEE YOU OUTSIDE
THE THEATER?

10:06.039 --> 10:08.341
- EVERY THURSDAY AND FRIDAY
DURING PREVIEWS,

10:08.375 --> 10:11.144
SOMEONE LEFT RED ROSES.

10:11.178 --> 10:13.380
NO CARD.

10:13.413 --> 10:19.186
I JUST THOUGHT THEY WERE
BEING SWEET.

10:21.789 --> 10:25.025
- THE LAST MULTIPLE
TICKET BUYER--ESTELLE ROBERTS.

10:25.058 --> 10:26.660
- YOU THINK A WOMAN DID THIS?
- I DON'T KNOW.

10:26.694 --> 10:29.730
SHE BOUGHT TICKETS FOUR NIGHTS
A WEEK DURING PREVIEWS.

10:29.763 --> 10:32.432
- PROBABLY JUST
SOME ACTOR'S MOTHER.

10:32.465 --> 10:36.169
- DANTE WHO?
- DANTE'S INFERNO.

10:36.203 --> 10:39.873
A PLAY CALLED NINE CIRCLES.
NINE CIRCLES OF HELL.

10:39.907 --> 10:42.209
- I DON'T KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

10:42.242 --> 10:43.677
I LIVE IN HELL.

10:43.711 --> 10:45.178
I DON'T NEED
TO SEE A PLAY ABOUT IT.

10:45.212 --> 10:46.914
- A DINER'S CARD
IN YOUR NAME

10:46.947 --> 10:50.183
WAS USED TO PURCHASE SINGLE
TICKETS ON 12 DIFFERENT NIGHTS.

10:50.217 --> 10:51.351
- WELL, IT WASN'T ME.

10:51.384 --> 10:53.286
- I DON'T EVEN HAVE
A DINER'S CARD.

10:53.320 --> 10:56.023
- WELL, THIS ADDRESS MATCHES
ONE ON FILE AT THE COMPANY.

10:56.056 --> 11:00.327
THE ACCOUNT'S BEEN OPEN
TWO YEARS, PAID ON TIME.

11:00.360 --> 11:03.030
- ANYBODY ELSE LIVE
IN THE HOUSE, MRS. ROBERTS?

11:03.063 --> 11:04.798
- MY SON JASON.

11:04.832 --> 11:06.433
HE DOESN'T HAVE
ANY CREDIT CARDS EITHER.

11:06.466 --> 11:08.268
- MAYBE WE COULD ASK HIM.

11:08.301 --> 11:10.904
- HE'S NOT HOME.
- IS THIS JASON'S ROOM?

11:10.938 --> 11:15.909
- YES, BUT HE DOESN'T LIKE
STRANGERS LOOKING AT HIS THINGS.

11:22.783 --> 11:25.018
- YEAH, I CAN SEE WHY.

11:25.052 --> 11:26.787
- HE HASN'T DONE
ANYTHING WRONG.

11:26.820 --> 11:29.322
HE TAKES A LOT OF PICTURES
OF HIS GIRLFRIEND.

11:29.356 --> 11:31.124
- BENSON AND AMARO.

11:31.158 --> 11:33.761
THIS IS FROM TODAY.

11:33.794 --> 11:36.063
HE'S GOT MEGHAN'S APARTMENT
BUGGED.

11:36.096 --> 11:40.768
- YOUR SON--
WHERE IS HE NOW?

11:47.975 --> 11:50.978
- [on video] I'LL BET
HE'S WATCHING US RIGHT NOW.

11:59.252 --> 12:00.788
- WAIT, THIS IS
FREAKING ME OUT.

12:00.821 --> 12:03.891
MY KITCHEN. MY BEDROOM.

12:03.924 --> 12:05.292
I DON'T UNDERSTAND.
WHO TOOK THESE?

12:05.325 --> 12:08.161
- DO YOU KNOW A JASON ROBERTS?

12:08.195 --> 12:10.764
- JASON?

12:10.798 --> 12:12.265
YEAH, HE'S MY I.T. GUY.

12:12.299 --> 12:15.102
- HE'S ALSO YOUR STALKER.

12:15.135 --> 12:18.906
- HE PUT CAMERAS
IN MY APARTMENT?

12:18.939 --> 12:21.842
- MEGHAN,
HOW'D YOU MEET JASON?

12:21.875 --> 12:25.112
- A GIRL IN MY ACTING CLASS
SET ME UP WITH HIM.

12:25.145 --> 12:26.346
HE HELPED ME
DESIGN MY WEBSITE.

12:26.379 --> 12:28.348
NEVER EVEN CHARGED ME.

12:28.381 --> 12:31.118
- JASON BOUGHT A TICKET
TO THE SHOW THE OTHER NIGHT.

12:31.151 --> 12:32.820
DID YOU INVITE HIM?

12:32.853 --> 12:35.956
- NO.

12:35.989 --> 12:38.025
I DIDN'T EVEN KNOW
HE WAS THERE.

12:38.058 --> 12:41.428
- SO YOU CAN'T TELL US
IF HE'S THE ONE WHO RAPED YOU.

12:41.461 --> 12:46.900
- I DON'T THINK SO.

12:46.934 --> 12:49.036
HE SEEMS SO HARMLESS.
HE'S KINDA SWEET.

12:49.069 --> 12:52.239
- HE VIDEOTAPED YOU
WHILE YOU SLEPT.

12:52.272 --> 12:53.573
WHILE YOU SHOWERED.

12:53.606 --> 12:55.508
- OH, MY--

12:55.542 --> 12:57.244
DID YOU ARREST HIM?

12:57.277 --> 12:58.478
- WELL, HE KNOWS THAT WE'RE
LOOKING FOR HIM,

12:58.511 --> 13:00.447
BUT, UM, BUT HE HASN'T
BEEN HOME YET.

13:00.480 --> 13:03.984
- SO HOW DO YOU GET IN TOUCH
WITH HIM--EMAIL, TEXT?

13:04.017 --> 13:05.285
- I CALL HIM.

13:05.318 --> 13:08.188
HE ALWAYS CALLS RIGHT BACK.
- GOOD.

13:08.221 --> 13:09.589
BECAUSE IF YOU'RE UP FOR IT,

13:09.622 --> 13:13.160
WE WANNA SET UP A MEETING
WITH YOU TWO.

13:13.193 --> 13:16.296
- DOES HE KNOW THAT I KNOW
ABOUT THE CAMERAS?

13:16.329 --> 13:19.066
- MAYBE YOU CAN CONVINCE HIM
THAT IT DOESN'T MATTER.

13:24.137 --> 13:28.341
IF IT'S TOO MUCH,
WE'LL FIGURE OUT ANOTHER WAY.

13:49.562 --> 13:51.899
- JASON, YOU CAME.

13:51.932 --> 13:56.103
- YOU SAID YOU NEEDED ME.

13:56.136 --> 13:58.271
I SHOULDN'T EVEN BE HERE.

13:58.305 --> 14:00.440
THE COPS, THEY CAME
TO MY APARTMENT.

14:00.473 --> 14:02.175
MY MOM'S FREAKING OUT.

14:02.209 --> 14:04.945
- I TOLD THEM
YOU'RE A GOOD GUY.

14:04.978 --> 14:08.048
I WANNA HEAR YOUR SIDE.

14:08.081 --> 14:10.050
- OKAY, ABOUT THOSE CAMERAS,
I CAN EXPLAIN.

14:10.083 --> 14:12.852
THEY'RE FOR SECURITY--
- HEY, JASON. ON YOUR FEET.

14:14.988 --> 14:16.890
- YOU SET ME UP?

14:16.924 --> 14:19.893
- YOU SPIED ON ME
IN THE SHOWER.

14:19.927 --> 14:21.895
WHAT ELSE DID YOU DO?

14:21.929 --> 14:23.964
- WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?
- LIKE YOU DON'T KNOW.

14:23.997 --> 14:25.165
- I DIDN'T DO ANYTHING.
I LOVE HER.

14:25.198 --> 14:26.366
- OH, PLEASE.

14:26.399 --> 14:27.367
- LET'S TALK ABOUT IT
AT THE PRECINCT.

14:27.400 --> 14:29.469
- YOU LOOK PRETTY.

14:31.404 --> 14:33.173
- HEY.
- I GOT UPSET, I'M SORRY.

14:33.206 --> 14:34.507
- NO, IT'S ALL RIGHT.

14:34.541 --> 14:36.076
YOU DID GOOD.

14:36.109 --> 14:39.346
REAL GOOD.

14:41.982 --> 14:44.117
- I INSTALLED THOSE CAMERAS
FOR SECURITY

14:44.151 --> 14:45.452
TO MAKE SURE MEGHAN
WAS SAFE.

14:45.485 --> 14:48.388
- FROM WHAT?
SLIPPING IN THE SHOWER?

14:48.421 --> 14:51.291
- SHE'S SO BEAUTIFUL.

14:51.324 --> 14:52.993
THERE'S A LOT OF CREEPS
OUT THERE.

14:53.026 --> 14:55.528
SHE'S TRUSTING.
AND I WATCH HER TO PROTECT HER.

14:55.562 --> 14:58.198
