- IT WAS MY AUDITION!

39:20.426 --> 39:22.494
SHE JUST CAME
TO HELP ME RUN LINES,

39:22.528 --> 39:24.696
AND AS SOON AS TED SAW HER,

39:24.730 --> 39:29.835
HE WANTED HER.

39:29.868 --> 39:33.605
AND YOU DIDN'T SAY NO.

39:35.641 --> 39:40.512
DO YOU KNOW WHAT I HAD TO DO
FOR THAT AUDITION?

39:40.546 --> 39:44.015
DOWN ON MY KNEES
WITH THAT PIG,

39:44.049 --> 39:46.652
AND WITH CRANE
AND ALL THOSE GUYS.

39:46.685 --> 39:50.689
AND I AM SO TIRED OF BEING
THE UGLY DUCKLING.

39:50.722 --> 39:54.493
AND I WANTED YOU TO KNOW
WHAT IT FELT LIKE

39:54.526 --> 39:57.763
TO FEEL DIRTY AND USED.

39:57.796 --> 40:00.499
TO WANT TO GIVE UP.

40:04.736 --> 40:06.905
- HOLLY...

40:06.938 --> 40:10.141
I THOUGHT YOU WERE MY FRIEND.

40:10.175 --> 40:14.045
YOU HAD SOMEONE RAPE ME!

40:14.079 --> 40:17.649
- IT'S ABOUT TIME SOMETHING BAD
HAPPENED IN YOUR LIFE.

40:17.683 --> 40:19.718
DON'T YOU THINK?

40:23.555 --> 40:25.423
- OKAY.

40:38.537 --> 40:42.974
I DIDN'T SEE OR HEAR
A SHRED OF REMORSE.

40:45.544 --> 40:47.979
WITH ALL THE ABUSIVE MEN
IN HER LIFE,

40:48.013 --> 40:50.682
AND MEGHAN'S BETRAYED
BY A WOMAN.

40:55.687 --> 40:57.489
DIDN'T SEE IT COMING.

40:57.523 --> 40:58.924
- YEAH, IT'S HARD ENOUGH
OUT THERE.

40:58.957 --> 41:02.961
YOU'D LIKE TO THINK THAT WE
COULD LOOK OUT FOR EACH OTHER.

41:05.564 --> 41:06.932
GOOD NIGHT.

41:08.900 --> 41:11.603
- GET HOME SAFE.
